---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "@/components/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  SEOTitle="AI Operations Platform | PrincipalAI"
  SEODescription="Secure AI deployment and workflow orchestration for private, controlled, and traceable AI systems."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#071f3f] via-[#123f86] to-[#e8f4ff] px-8 py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-100">
        AI Operations Platform
      </p>
      <h1 class="max-w-5xl font-serif text-5xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-6xl">
        Secure AI operations for organisations that need control.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
        The AI Operations Platform helps organisations deploy, manage, and govern AI workflows in controlled environments.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700"
      >
        Request a demonstration
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            The problem
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            AI adoption needs more than model access.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Many organisations want to use AI but cannot rely on public tools for sensitive information, regulated workflows, or internal analytical systems.
          </p>
          <p>
            The AI Operations Platform provides the operational layer for secure deployment, workflow orchestration, access control, and traceable use of AI across professional environments.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
          What it supports
        </p>
        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          Private AI systems built around organisational workflows.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Secure deployment</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Deploy AI systems in controlled environments aligned with organisational privacy and security requirements.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Workflow orchestration</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Connect AI assistants, models, documents, dashboards, and analytical tools into repeatable workflows.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Access and governance</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Support user roles, controlled access, human review, and governance over AI-enabled processes.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Traceable outputs</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Improve confidence in AI use through structured workflows, review points, and clearer output provenance.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Typical use cases
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Operational AI for high-trust environments.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Internal AI assistants for research, policy, and technical advisory teams.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Private knowledge systems connected to organisational documents and models.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            AI workflows for reporting, evidence synthesis, and analytical quality assurance.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Controlled deployment of AI tools across projects, teams, and secure environments.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Why PrincipalAI
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            AI operations shaped by real analytical work.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            PrincipalAI designs operational AI systems for organisations that need practical capability, not experimentation alone.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our approach connects AI with evidence, modelling, reporting, and governance so that teams can use AI in ways that are useful, controlled, and defensible.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#071f3f] px-8 py-20 text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Deploy AI with control, traceability, and purpose.
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
          Talk to PrincipalAI about secure AI deployment, workflow orchestration, and private AI operations.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700"
        >
          Request a demonstration
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
